fields.template_css_field: .navbar-gradient { background: no-repeat fixed linear-gradient(90deg, #111111, #111111); border-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #111111, #111111); } .navbar-text-color { color: #DDDDDD !important; border-left: 1px #DDDDDD solid; } li ul li .navbar-text-color { border-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,0,0,0), rgba(255,0,0,0)); } .dropdown-menu { border: 1px #DDDDDD solid; } .navbar-text-color:hover { color: white !important; background-color: #2B2B2B !important; } .body-gradient { background: no-repeat fixed linear-gradient(90deg, #1C1C1C, #1C1C1C); } .body-text-color { color: #DDDDDD; } .footer-color { background-color: #141414 !important; } .footer-text-color { color: #DDDDDD; } .button-text-color { background-color: #DB7500; color: #DDDDDD; } .button-text-color:hover { color: white; background-color: #2B84BF; }
